# 📄 Functional Design Document (FDD)

## TechnoPath — SEAIT Campus Guide System

**Version:** 4.0 (PWA + Django Backend)  
**Institution:** South East Asian Institute of Technology (SEAIT), Tupi, South Cotabato  
**Date:** April 3, 2026  

---

## 1. System Title & Overview

**TechnoPath** is a Progressive Web Application (PWA) that serves as an interactive campus navigation and information system for SEAIT. It allows students, faculty, and visitors to explore campus buildings, view interactive floor plans, get turn-by-turn navigation routes, interact with an AI chatbot for campus queries, receive department announcements, and submit feedback — all from a mobile browser with full offline support.

The system is composed of three tiers:

| Tier | Technology | Purpose |
|------|-----------|---------|
| **Frontend PWA** | Vue 3 + Vite + Pinia + IndexedDB (Dexie) | Mobile-first guest interface & Desktop admin panel |
| **Primary Backend** | Django 4 + Django REST Framework + SQLite | REST API, authentication (JWT), RBAC, CRUD operations |
| **Chatbot Service** | Flask (Python) + SQLite | Rule-based campus Q&A chatbot |

### Architecture

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Vue 3 PWA (Mobile Guest + Admin)    │
│  IndexedDB for offline caching       │
└──────────┬───────────────────────────┘
           │  REST / JWT
┌──────────▼───────────────────────────┐
│  Django REST Framework Backend       │
│  SQLite: technopath.db               │
│  Apps: users, facilities, rooms,     │
│        navigation, chatbot, notifs,  │
│        feedback, announcements, core │
└──────────┬───────────────────────────┘
           │
┌──────────▼───────────────────────────┐
│  Flask Chatbot Microservice          │
│  SQLite: chatbot.db                  │
│  Port 5000                           │
└──────────────────────────────────────┘
```

