## 2. User Roles

| Role Key | Display Name | Scope |
|----------|-------------|-------|
| `super_admin` | Safety and Security Office | Full system access — single account |
| `dean` | College Dean | Per-department account — approves announcements, views audits/feedback |
| `program_head` | College Program Head | Per-program account — manages own rooms, posts announcements |
| `basic_ed_head` | Basic Education Head | Basic Ed department — manages own rooms, posts announcements |
| *Guest* | Student / Faculty / Visitor | Unauthenticated — browse map, navigate, use chatbot, view notifications |

